CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

November 10, 2010

[Cite as 11/1012010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-5433.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

1990-2539. Disciplinary Counsel v. Conley.

This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing by respondent, Bernard Carl Conley, of an affidavit of compliance and a motion to purge contempt. Upon consideration thereof,

It is ordered by the court that the motion to purge contempt is granted.
